Nav rem vaz
Dum special_factorial(n):
   Kem fact_i par 1
   Kem special_fact par 1
   Kem i par 1
   Mup dum n pag:
      Kem fact_i par 積(fact_i, i)
      Kem special_fact par 積(special_fact, fact_i)
      Rav i
   Dam mup
   Dup vem special_fact
Pam dum
>>> special_factorial(4) 
288
>>> special_factorial(4) 
288
>>> special_factorial(5) 
34560
>>> special_factorial(7) 
125411328000
>>> special_factorial(1) 
1